cede_le_passage.name: Yield
cede_le_passage.description: Indicates that drivers must yield to vehicles on the main road.

priorite.description: Indicates that the road has priority over secondary roads. Drivers must yield to vehicles coming from these roads.

stop.name: Stop
stop.description: Requires drivers to come to a complete stop before proceeding. Priority must be yielded to vehicles on the main road.
